[inaudible] to run forever.

00:08:27.740 --> 00:08:31.680
In Israel, these are the
Israelis who come and flock

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:35.350
as I said, to the venues
and we have a very intense,

00:08:35.350 --> 00:08:41.760
some may say, maybe a bit of
inflation, very intense scene

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:44.350
and it is very diverse
as I've said.

00:08:44.350 --> 00:08:48.070
We have shows not only in
Hebrew, but also in Arabic,

00:08:48.070 --> 00:08:51.570
Yiddish, in Amharic,
in Russian, in English

00:08:51.570 --> 00:08:54.810
and I think it's just a
matter of time until we have,

00:08:54.810 --> 00:08:58.610
we'll find that we'll
also add shows in French

00:08:58.610 --> 00:09:02.050
