to Israel in recent years.

00:09:02.050 --> 00:09:05.990
Israel is very unique,
we have some kind

00:09:05.990 --> 00:09:11.300
of abnormalities I think or some
very specific characteristics

00:09:11.300 --> 00:09:13.090
which I think I'd
like to point out.

00:09:13.090 --> 00:09:15.970
First of all, I don't,
to best of my knowledge,

00:09:15.970 --> 00:09:18.680
I think Israel is the only
country in the world to have,

00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:22.070
for example, it's national
theater established long ago

00:09:22.070 --> 00:09:25.370
before the establishment of
the actual state, you know,

00:09:25.370 --> 00:09:28.540
our national theater,
Habima which I come from,

00:09:28.540 --> 00:09:32.290
was established in 1917
in Moscow, in Russia,

00:09:32.290 --> 00:09:34.550
whereas the state of
Israel came to life

00:09:34.550 --> 00:09:38.070
in 1948, some 31 years later.

00:09:38.070 --> 00:09:41.240
Israel is the only country
in the world to have,

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:45.880
to have its national theater not
functioning in the capital city

00:09:45.880 --> 00:09:48.320
of Jerusalem, but in Tel Aviv.

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:56.490
Jerusalem is not yet ready
for the revolution of theater.

00:09:56.490 --> 00:09:59.550
And, Israel is, as I've said,
is really in love with theater

00:09:59.550 --> 00:10:02.180
and I think this might
be explained by the fact

00:10:02.180 --> 00:10:08.390
that theater is relatively a
new phenomena to Jewish culture,

00:10:08.390 --> 00:10:11.290
Jewish culture and Jewish
life, whereas the rest

00:10:11.290 --> 00:10:14.530
of the Western world have
been experiencing theater ever

00:10:14.530 --> 00:10:20.040
since Ancient Greece, you
know, some 2,500 years ago.

00:10:20.040 --> 00:10:24.770
Jews started dealing or enjoying

00:10:24.770 --> 00:10:28.140
or practicing theater
less than 200 years ago.

00:10:28.140 --> 00:10:30.940
We are very new to the business
and I think that in comparison

00:10:30.940 --> 00:10:34.370
to ordinations, the fact
that we are very new to it,

00:10:34.370 --> 00:10:37.360
maybe explains why we are still
very much in love with it.

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:40.110
Whereas, the rest of the
world, you know, came to terms

00:10:40.110 --> 00:10:45.100
with theater, it's one way
among other forms of, you know,

00:10:45.100 --> 00:10:49.660
of a day or a night outside.

00:10:49.660 --> 00:10:53.930
Israel is very much
celebrating the fact

00:10:53.930 --> 00:10:58.940
that we are finally allowed to
enjoy an evening in the theater,

00:10:58.940 --> 00:11:03.980
because for many, many,
generations, the orthodox,

00:11:03.980 --> 00:11:07.170
Jewish authorities rejected
the sheer concept of theater.

00:11:07.170 --> 00:11:10.100
Theater was something which
was identified with then,

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:13.270
with the gentiles something
which is not done, you know.

00:11:13.270 --> 00:11:16.090
Jews had been thanking the
Lord for many generations

00:11:16.090 --> 00:11:21.580
for making them [inaudible]
yeshivas and synagogues and not

00:11:21.580 --> 00:11:24.800
of this [inaudible] of mockers
as they call the theater.

00:11:24.800 --> 00:11:30.850
They're not going to theaters
or to circuses, God forbid.

00:11:30.850 --> 00:11:37.410
So, and some 150
or 200 years ago,

00:11:37.410 --> 00:11:41.800
as part of what we call
the national renaissance,

00:11:41.800 --> 00:11:45.530
[inaudible] the national
secular revolution

00:11:45.530 --> 00:11:51.890
which took part some 150 years
ago, theater actually managed

00:11:51.890 --> 00:11:54.030
to put its foot in the door

00:11:54.030 --> 00:11:58.280
and we started practicing
theater as well.

00:11:58.280 --> 00:12:00.580
At the beginning, just
for your knowledge,

00:12:00.580 --> 00:12:03.500
it was allowed only one
day in the Jewish calendar,

00:12:03.500 --> 00:12:06.560
we already have one,
how do you say,

00:12:06.560 --> 00:12:11.200
one day which is freaky and, you
know, pulling and they allowed,

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:15.700
if you want to do your shows,
use this day of the year

00:12:15.700 --> 00:12:18.810
where we, we get drunk
and we change costumes

00:12:18.810 --> 00:12:20.630
and do your shows
during that day,

00:12:20.630 --> 00:12:22.530
